y drawback of this product is that it is only compatible with Samsung Galaxy devices. So if you've been looking to keep better track of your things, then the Samsung SmartTag 2 is going to be the one to get. Just be sure to act quickly as this deal won't be around for too long. And if you aren't sure, be sure to check out our other smart tag recommendations.",
